high_descs: Turn around and go forward, then turn right and go toward the dishwasher, then turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, take out the potato from inside, then close the microwave.

Open the fridge, put the potato inside and chill it, then take the potato out.
Go to the microwave to your right.
Open the microwave, put the potato inside, then close it.

Pick up the potato in the microwave.
